<Body>
	<Title>江苏丹阳近百学生食物中毒 警方展开调查</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2002年12月7日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="absTime">2002年12月5日上午</Time>，<Location lid="l1">江苏镇江丹阳市皇塘镇吴塘初级中学</Location>发生学生集体<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2,s3,s4">近百名学生</Participant>因为<Denoter did="d2" type="action">吃</Denoter>了<Object oid="o2">学校食堂的早餐</Object></Event>后<Event eid="e3"><Denoter did="d3" type="perception">恶心</Denoter></Event>、<Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="action">呕吐</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">其中<Participant sid="s5,s6">4名严重者</Participant>甚至<Denoter did="d5" type="action">抽搐</Denoter></Event>、<Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">昏迷</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e7">据<Denoter did="d7" type="statement">了解</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8"><Object oid="o8">吴塘中学</Object>今年将初中部和高中部<Denoter did="d8" type="action">分开</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="emergency">发生</Denoter>此次<Object oid="o9">中毒事件</Object>的是<Location lid="l9"> 吴塘初级中学</Location></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>该校共有28个班级、1000多名学生，其中寄宿生有200多人。<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">当日上午</Time>，<Participant sid="s10">寄宿生们</Participant>和往常一样到<Location lid="l10">学校食堂</Location><Denoter did="d10" type="action">就餐</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">食堂</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="statement">提供</Denoter>的<Object oid="o11">早餐</Object>有稀饭、包子、馒头、月饼、榨菜</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12,s13,s14">学生们</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="action">吃</Denoter>完了<Object oid="o12">早餐</Object></Event><Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">上早读课</Denoter>时</Event>，<Event eid="e14">陆续<Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>了脸色苍白、肚子疼痛、恶心、呕吐等<Object oid="o14">症状</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e15"><Participant sid="s15" type="agent">学校老师</Participant>见状赶紧将<Participant oid="o15" type="recipient">他们</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="movement">送到</Denoter>了<Location lid="l15" type="destination">附近的皇塘卫生院</Location></Event><Event eid="e16"><Denoter did="d16" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>中毒学生越来越多，<Event eid="e17">到<Time tid="t17" type="relTime">8时30分左右</Time>，已有<Participant sid="s17">近百名学生</Participant>被<Denoter did="d17" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l17" type="destination">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e18"><Denoter did="d18" type="operation">急救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e19">其中有<Participant sid="s19,s20,s21,s22">三女一男</Participant>由于<Denoter did="d19" type="action">抽搐</Denoter>时间过长</Event><Event eid="e20">已<Denoter did="d20" type="stateChange">昏迷</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e21">被<Denoter did="d21" type="movement">急送</Denoter><Location lid="l21">丹阳人民医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e23"><Participant sid="s23">据吴塘初级中学办公室主任江涛</Participant><Denoter did="d23" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，据统计，<Event eid="e24">有<Participant sid="s24">近百名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d24" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter>了</Event>，学校一天都没有上课。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e25">该事件具体原因还在<Denoter did="d25" type="operation">调查</Denoter>当中</Event>，<Event eid="e26"><Participant sid="s26">警方</Participant>已经将<Object oid="o26">早餐的食物</Object><Denoter did="d26" type="operation">取样</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e27">进行<Denoter did="d27" type="operation">化验</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>学校食堂是承包出去的，<Event eid="e28"><Participant oid="o28" type="recipient">承包人</Participant>已被<Participant sid="s28" type="agent">警方</Participant><Denoter did="d28" type="action">带走</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
